itationally confined\ndetonation\" occurring at a later epoch, but additional burning will occur\nfollowing breakout that may modify this conclusion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2013 17:26:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Dec 2013 20:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
