ignificant effect on the evolution and fragmentation of the gas in\nthe halo - in particular, we find that at least 64 grid cells are needed to\ncover the Jeans length in order to properly resolve the fragmentation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2013 20:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-24"}
